{"type": "article", "id": 27413, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-05-27T06:53:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 28208, "name": "满月"}, {"id": 28209, "name": "Whaletone"}, {"id": 28210, "name": "Plantereo"}, {"id": 28211, "name": "Isla"}, {"id": 15891, "name": "意外设计"}, {"id": 28212, "name": "Caterina Moretti"}, {"id": 28213, "name": "Seungji Mun"}, {"id": 28214, "name": "Miron Lior"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132210Pp9Mq0Whlc6ArfFo.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p>\r\n<p>          </p>\r\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\r\n<h2>满月 by 意外设计</h2>\r\n<p>古时人们常以圆月来寄托思乡之情，由设计师黄国栋创立的的<a href=\"http://ey-products.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">意外设计</a>以此为灵感推出了这款名为满月的台灯。外壳采用榉木制作，内置的 LED 灯从中间透出温暖的光线，内侧面还添加了一个可插入植物的小孔，在枝叶的搭配下看起来更诗情画意。这是它的<a href=\"http://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.1.w6048809-4031259655.6.8zAHVl&amp;id=35208151201\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 498 元。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160035FDaKbk9IPXy4z5u3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160035iuWc6rHRtxsG1qS8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160036XIfuEAtUbqNsziC5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160036NqhvyPjLRuQaVfrx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69066667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160037RwH5soScJY9p8LAn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63066667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160037DKPzL6Jg4EIx2pHj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Whaletone by Whaletone Ltd</h2>\r\n<p>你有没有幻想过未来的钢琴会是什么样？最近波兰设计师 <a href=\"http://www.robertmajkut.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Robert Majkut</a> 根据自己的一个梦设计了这款名为 Whaletone 的<a href=\"http://www.whaletone.com/products/royal-digital\" rel=\"nofollow\">数码钢琴</a>，外型就好像是鲸鱼出水时那样有着流畅的曲线。优雅的造型和钢琴悠扬的声音结合，带给人全新的视听感受，也是对现有钢琴设计的一种挑战。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160038pOKUsCfi5zXSl90Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82191781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160039QiU50Me32Fst4B1A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82191781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160039TRJ3aCZuPNg19SyY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82191781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160040dX5wNJIijbPH3Dvt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82191781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160040tRwjKirEeAPZVngx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82191781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Plantereo by Plantereo team</h2>\r\n<p>由于在城市中种植花草的空间非常有限，<a href=\"http://www.plantereo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Plantereo</a> 的设计团队推出了这款既能节约空间又可以防止你忘记为植物浇水的多功能花盆。如果你打算将 Plantereo 玻璃罩用作储水盆使用，将植物移植到白色的花盆前需要在盆底的小洞中穿上一根灯芯。这样一来，植物可以通过灯芯自动吸收水盆里的水，最长可以持续五天不需要额外浇灌。如果你对这个小巧又实用的花盆感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/plantereo/plantereo-a-convertible-self-watering-planter-and\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 45 美元。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160041Vx2NaCiMBJAh9k3s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41470588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160041LzVbGwY7oq3St5ZU.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160044sVfZQpuiFB9taWYD.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160048DsSvbVZc2e1a4HLU.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\r\n<h2>Isla by Caterina Moretti</h2>\r\n<p>Peca 工作室的 Caterina Moretti 设计的这款边桌 <a href=\"http://www.peca.com.mx/#/isla/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Isla</a> 看上去就像是在一面平静的湖水中升起了一座小岛。边桌取材自实心橡木、黄铜、石灰石和大理石，在 Moretti 的精心设计下，这四种对比鲜明的材质融合在了一起，仿佛还原了一幅山水画。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kichink.com/buy/825371\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 911.68 美元。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021600508TZXEYBUqC5N2kef.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160051yuTi4E59hgK36IDq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160052wsGXeOCRjfiBcY7S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160052AeDojQsJfl1cEnNd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49791667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160053oFpswL6DNcgSJiuT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160054v8gHLbRerJip03za.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Dog house sofa by Seungji Mun</h2>\r\n<p>宠物也是家庭的一员，越来越多的设计师尝试着让家具能同时满足人类和宠物的需求。<a href=\"http://www.munseungji.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Seungji Mun</a> 设计的这张沙发与平时安置在家中其他地方的狗屋结合在了一起，开放的设计让狗狗们可以很方便地攀爬玩耍，同时也拉近了它们和主人间的距离，看上去非常温馨。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160054gOMJKFXP3GsdUHl0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160055igwlWxYdXmDELboz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160055NzbflD2K3R8eQXdc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160056o7dr42ZGKuScxJ6y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021600566gkzOtH9vm0FdbGx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160057S7pMWa4nfPIeHsFC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 30px; text-align: left; background-color: transparent;\">Conceal book shelf by Miron Lior</span></h2>\r\n<p>想让书像是被施展了魔法那样“悬浮”起来？Miron Lior 为家具品牌 umbra 设计的隐形书架会让拜访你家的客人大吃一惊。书架呈字母 L 造型，水平端下方隐藏的小钩可以夹住最下面的一本书的封底，固定之后就可以把书往上摆了。根据不同的尺寸，最高可以承受 13 千克的重量。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.umbra.com/usd/wall-decor/shelves-boards/conceal-floating-shelf-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价从 13 到 18 美元不等。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160058iqRVXSUIkwAhcZpP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.98796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160100gxhBCzwOZ1Hpsn63.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160100u0sX5rIqKyPnTWvx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160101iCXjdLgZDQlYKG6w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>"}